  lines:
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: What is weird about it?
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I mean\u2026 I am literally going to touch you."
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: I am just a lamp. That is how it work.
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: No, this whole thing is weird!
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: You are making it weird.
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Okay, then what are your pronouns?
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: My what?
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Your pronouns.
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "I am a genie in a fucking lamp. I don\u2019t even have a gender."
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: So you are agender?
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Nooo
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: ...
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: ...........
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Wait.
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Maybe?
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Okay, I need to think about that later. Just rub me first.
  options:
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    replyText: (Sign) FIne.
